{"tid":1534193,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［罷工討論］其實今日仲係咪罷工？","createTime":"2019-09-03T02:32:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-03T03:59:28.000Z","uid":9845,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"21e5ddaed7c62a2b7b3bb2283b12807277c0791e","tid":1534193,"uid":9845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T02:32:33.000Z","msg":"老老豆豆，其實而加一般市民罷工係完全無意義<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n要罷工有影響力，一定係工業罷工 eg 航空，鐵路，巴士<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申：文員仔 全公司得自己罷工 琴日去完去集會圍爐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ccf8aeab3544c827a5e6eb442ec776a274e0d5a","tid":1534193,"uid":69525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T02:32:46.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: small;\">我唔想知佢錄音內容<br />\n我推到同溫層既大家知道<br />\n你地負責幫手去fb啊等等宣傳得唔得<br />\n唔好再理膠post喇 關注返行動post<br />\n再好好運用6月至今每個核彈去twitter做文宣喇<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/twitter4HK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Ftwitter4HK&d=xz9%2BKahtnlDLfwjNDOwuFBckzRVyZutP2gug%2B5Lqx%2Fc%3D&h=146d5162\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/twitter4HK</a><br />\n<br />\n[置頂] 建議9月8日百萬人大遊行/集會，<br />\n請求美國國會通過人權及民主法案<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1530650\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1530650</a><br />\n<br />\n901 機場測試係成功<br />\n辛苦曬行左20公里既手足 勿被帶風向<br />\n<br />\n908 我希望美國巴絲手足都有遊行<br />\n聲援香港同埋同要請求美國國會通過人權法!<br />\n<br />\n908 建議：<br />\n-大量英文文宣/紙牌<br />\n-高舉大量美國議員大頭相<br />\n-高舉大量國旗<br />\n-唔建議勇武，因為主題涉及美國<br />\n(另一原因係 廢時佢又區區有狗搜身兼 補充文具需時又珍貴)<br />\n-領事館門前唱國歌<br />\n<br />\n無人申請不反 都要照上街<br />\n需要文宣制圖 然後我幫你宣傳<br />\n由今日開始宣! 908照上街!<br />\n<br />\n建議內容copy某位巴打既<br />\n9月我要照上街<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>"},{"pid":"efba52c78b605ceae3392d6df938c8625d74049a","tid":1534193,"uid":9845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy